OL,5, Three statues thought to be the first  
OL,6, sculptures depicting black British     
OL,7, people on display in England are set to
OL,8, return to Brixton station later.       
OL,10,FThe life-size bronze figures, called   
OL,11,FPlatforms Piece, were first installed  
OL,12,Fon the platform in 1986 before being   
OL,13,Fremoved in 2016 for refurbishment.     
OL,15,FCreated by Kevin Atherton, it depicts  
OL,16,Fthree Brixton residents of the time and
OL,17,Fis Grade II listed.                    
OL,19,FThe original statues will be joined by 
OL,20,Fa new one named Joy II.                
